        <mj-text padding="0">
          <h2><a href="https://www.example.com" style="color:#006837;">Ray Has Big Ideas for Texas</a></h2>
          <p style="font-size:16px;">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Morbi adipiscing convallis
            vitae quisque commodo volutpat ut. Cursus sed quam ornare augue
            quis metus. Fermentum sit id pharetra tortor. In viverra semper et
